弊」、多名员工被罚，内部人士证实 - 上游新闻 汇聚向上的力量"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-6471236ae60f1bf02f8742517b5dffb2_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "99 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/14693890972"}}, "attached_info": "CkIIqovHzKrI1KseEAMaCTExMzkxNzM0MCCSnMC+BjAAOIwEQA5yCzE0NjkzODkwOTcyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1741793182.919356", "card_id": "Q_2346959097", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "郭芙对杨过说「你宝贝师父自己做的事，她自己才知道」 ，为什么会被杨过打耳光？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "郭芙之前听到赵志敬的说法。而在赵志敬的话里面，小龙女并没有做什么，只有甄志丙在做什么。 那么为什么郭芙要说小龙女「做了什么」呢？ --- 郭芙续道：「我好奇心起，悄悄到窗外张望，只见两人已经收剑不斗了，但还在斗口。姓赵的说那姓尹的和你师父怎样怎样，姓尹的并不抵赖，只怪他不该大声叫嚷…」 杨过霍地揭开身上棉被，翻身坐在床沿，喝道：「甚么怎样怎样？」郭芙脸上微微一红，神色颇为尴尬，道：「我怎知道？难道还会是好事了？你宝贝师父自己做的事，她自己才知道。」语气之中，充满了轻蔑。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-0ed0e9659e7d10fbf6dbc36a23bcdf02_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "96 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2346959097"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIqovHzKrI1KseEAMaCTExMTQ0NjExOCCxg/24BjAAODRAD3IKMjM0Njk1OTA5N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1741793182.920220", "card_id": "Q_14734921529", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "李纨的父亲是国子监祭酒，为什么贾兰还要去教书这么差的学堂上课？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-9dd8d8ee114b03f99cafd38f8e344956_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "75 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https:/